ssinsider.com%2Fdoordash-history-milestones-food-delivery-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDoorDash%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20delivered%20products%20from%20Walmart%20stores%20to%20customers%20using%20its%20legion%20of%20independent%20contractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20month%2C%20Walmart%20acquired%20Delivery%20Drivers%20Inc.%2C%20the%20company%20it%20worked%20with%20to%20create%20Spark.%20Walmart%20and%20DDI%20have%20worked%20together%20since%202018.%20%26quot%3BHundreds%20of%20thousands%26quot%3B%20of%20Spark%20drivers%20have%20since%20made%20deliveries%20through%20the%20app%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.walmart.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F06%2F07%2Fthe-spark-driver-platform-celebrates-5-years-of-growth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWalmart%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20blog%20post%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20workers%20who%20have%20delivered%20or%20shopped%20orders%20for%20Spark%20say%20the%20service%20faces%20multiple%20problems.%20Some%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20customers%20who%20don't%20tip%2C%20are%20similar%20to%20those%20faced%20by%20contractors%20for%20other%20apps%2C%20such%20as%20DoorDash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%2C%20including%20Spark%20drivers%20who%20use%20multiple%20identities%2C%20appear%20to%20be%20worse%20on%20Spark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20roundup%20of%20Business%20Insider's%20coverage%20of%20Walmart's%20Spark%20delivery%20service%20over%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20for%20Spark%20and%20have%20a%20story%20idea%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20abitter%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFraudulent%20Walmart%20Spark%20drivers%20use%20false%20identities%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sometimes%20many%20identities%20at%20once%20%E2%80%94%20to%20claim%20orders.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202023%2C%20some%20Spark%20workers%20protested%20outside%20a%20Chicago-area%20Walmart%20to%20call%20attention%20to%20drivers%20who%20appear%20to%20be%20using%20false%20identities%20and%20special%20software%20to%20claim%20more%20orders%20than%20their%20peers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20maximize%20their%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20investigation%20into%20the%20claims%20found%20that%20some%20drivers%20were%20indeed%20showing%20up%20at%20Walmart%20stores%20around%20the%20US%20using%20multiple%20names%20that%20were%20not%20their%20own%20to%20claim%20orders.%20Walmart%20rolled%20out%20an%20identity-verification%20measure%20through%20the%20Spark%20app%2C%20but%20the%20problem%20has%20persisted%2C%20several%20Spark%20drivers%20have%20since%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20more%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-delivery-workers-say-their-jobs-are-being-stolen-by-bots-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20Walmart%20delivery%20driver%20said%20his%20weekly%20earnings%20dropped%20from%20%241%2C500%20to%20%24200%20due%20to%20competition%20from%20bots%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20a%20growing%20problem%2C%20workers%20say%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20more%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-spark-delivery-app-multiple-accounts-names-verify-identity-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWalmart's%20delivery%20program%20is%20having%20an%20identity%20crisis.%20Some%20drivers%20aren't%20who%20they%20say%20they%20are.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20more%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-spark-delivery-accounts-go-for-hundreds-dollars-social-media-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESome%20Walmart%20delivery%20drivers%20are%20buying%20their%20credentials%20online%20%E2%80%94%20letting%20anyone%20deliver%20goods%20to%20your%20door%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWalmart%20Spark%20drivers%20deal%20with%20long%20wait%20times%20for%20orders%20and%20customers%20asking%20them%20to%20bring%20deliveries%20into%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fh2%