EThis%20as-told-to%20story%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Germaine%20Arenas%2C%20a%2027-year-old%20traveler%20and%20accounting%20analyst%20from%20Winnipeg%2C%20Canada.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20born%20in%20the%20Philippines%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsingapore-lifestyle-food-shopping-malls-weather-heat-misconceptions-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrew%20up%20in%20Singapore%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20moved%20to%20Canada%20when%20I%20was%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hadn't%20visited%20Singapore%20since%202010%20and%20wanted%20to%20show%20my%20boyfriend%20%E2%80%94%20who%20was%20also%20born%20in%20the%20Philippines%20and%20moved%20to%20Canada%20in%20his%2020s%20%E2%80%94%20where%20I%20grew%20up.%20So%20we%20planned%20a%20monthlong%20trip%20to%20the%20Philippines%20in%20September%2C%20with%20a%20two-day%20stopover%20in%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20live%20in%20Winnipeg%2C%20a%20city%20some%2062%20miles%20from%20the%20US-Canada%20border.%20Winnipeg%20International%20Airport%20isn't%20a%20main%20hub%20for%20international%20flights%2C%20so%20we%20had%20to%20take%20three%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20round-trip%20economy%20ticket%20from%20Winnipeg%20to%20Manila%2C%20including%20a%20stopover%20in%20Singapore%2C%20was%20%242%2C100.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20started%20with%20a%20flight%20on%20Air%20Canada%20from%20Winnipeg%20to%20Vancouver.%20From%20there%2C%20after%20a%20three-hour%20layover%2C%20we%20boarded%20a%2015-hour%20flight%20on%20Philippine%20Airlines%20to%20Manila%2C%20where%20we%20waited%20for%20four%20hours%20before%20boarding%20the%20last%20leg%20to%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20we%20traveled%20for%20some%2028%20hours%2C%20including%20layovers.%20While%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-pack-in-your-carry-on-for-a-long-haul-flight%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong-haul%20flights%3C%2Fa%3E%20aren't%20the%20most%20comfortable%2C%20I%20did%20the%20following%20three%20things%20to%20improve%20my%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FNIRjg%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Map%20of%20Germaine%20Arenas's%2028-hour%20trip%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22549%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Pack%20essentials%20to%20help%20you%20sleep%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20hard%20time%20sleeping%20on%20flights.%20As%20getting%20shut-eye%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fflight-attendants-tips-surviving-long-haul-flights-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong-haul%20flights%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20essential%2C%20I%20always%20pack%20melatonin%20supplements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20essential%20for%20me%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-noise-cancelling-headphones%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enoise-canceling%20earbuds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20was%20surrounded%20by%20kids%20and%20babies%20on%20the%20flight%20from%20Vancouver%20to%20Manila.%20Wearing%20earbuds%20made%20blocking%20out%20the%20noise%20on%20the%20plane%20easier%2C%20so%20I%20was%20well-rested%20despite%20the%20long%20travel.%20Other%20items%20like%20travel%20pillows%20and%20blankets%20could%20also%20help%20make%20a%20cramped%20seat%20more%20comfortable%2C%20especially%20when%20traveling%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%2014-hour%20time%20difference%20between%20Winnipeg%20and%20Singapore%2C%20but%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairline-ceo-on-working-as-flight-attendant-night-flight-challenging-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enight%20flight%3C%2Fa%3E%20helped%20minimize%20jet%20lag.%20Despite%20the%20red-eye%20fl