Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22884%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGermaine%20Arenas%20had%20to%20take%20a%20domestic%20flight%20from%20Winnipeg%20to%20Vancouver%20first%20before%20hopping%20on%20an%20international%20flight.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Germaine%20Arenas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Let%20others%20deplane%20first%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20long%20flight%2C%20most%20passengers%20are%20itching%20to%20get%20off%20the%20plane.%20I%20noticed%20many%20passengers%20tried%20to%20rush%20and%20squeeze%20between%20the%20plane's%20tight%20aisle%20to%20get%20off%20first.%20After%20several%20flights%2C%20it%20got%20frustrating%20and%20uncomfortable%2C%20especially%20when%20I%20was%20struggling%20to%20get%20my%20bags%2C%20as%20everyone%20else%20was%20trying%20to%20do%20so%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20learned%20to%20let%20others%20disembark%20first%20%E2%80%94%20this%20let%20me%20take%20my%20time%20when%20retrieving%20my%20bags.%20It%20also%20helped%20me%20stay%20relaxed%20on%20my%20daylong%20flights%20and%20avoid%20arguments%20with%20other%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanada-singapore-philippines-flight-airline-passenger-travel-cheap-tips-plane-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704028561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6576b34e0ec98e92f74df8d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanada-singapore-philippines-flight-airline-passenger-travel-cheap-tips-plane-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Germaine%20Arenas%20advises%20travelers%20to%20choose%20a%20red-eye%20flight%20when%20there's%20a%20big%20time%20difference.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mdescalsota%40insider.com%20(Marielle%20Descalsota)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanada-singapore-philippines-flight-airline-passenger-travel-cheap-tips-plane-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20China%20to%20OPEC%2B%2C%20here%20are%20the%20biggest%20wildcards%20that%20could%20jolt%20oil%20markets%20in%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221999%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22fracking%20crude%20oil%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f05e91c5c7b8c9a0cea35%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22999%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EANDREWS%2C%20TX%20-%20JANUARY%2020%3A%20An%20oil%20pumpjack%20works%20at%20dawn%20in%20the%20Permian%20Basin%20oil%20field%20on%20January%2020%2C%202016%20in%20the%20oil%20town%20of%20Andrews%2C%20Texas.%20Despite%20recent%20drops%20in%20the%20price%20of%20oil%2C%20many%20residents%20of%20Andrews%2C%20and%20similar%20towns%20across%20the%20Permian%2C%20are%20trying%20to%20take%20the%20long%20view%20and%20stay%20optimistic.%20The%20Dow%20Jones%20industrial%20average%20plunged%20540%20points%20on%20Wednesday%20after%20crude%20oil%20plummeted%20another%207%25%20and%20crashed%20below%20%2427%20a%20barrel%3Cp%3ESpencer%20Platt%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHeading%20into%202024%2C%20the%20biggest%20wildcards%20include%20demand%20from%20China%20and%20cohesion%20within%20OPEC%2B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUS%20oil%20production%20isn't%20expected%20to%20soar%20next%20year%20like%20it%20did%20in%202023.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECrude%20prices%20fell%2010%25%20in%202023%20as%20surging%20US%20supplies%20offset%20cuts%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20Russia.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECrude%20oil%20prices%20saw%20wild%20swings%20in%202023%20before%20finishing%20the%20year%20down%2010%25%2C%20and%20more%20volatility%20could%20be%20ahead%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20forces%20driving%20oil%20markets%20delivered%20big%20surprises%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20and%20they%20represent%20major%20sources%20of%20uncertainty%20in%20the%20new%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20analysts%2C%20here's%20what%20could%20jostle%20the%20oil%20market%2C%20from%20OPEC's%20weakening%20control%20over%20prices%20to%20China's%20economic%20slowdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOPEC%2B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cartel%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Foil-outlook-market-opec-cuts-crude-prices-us-production-boom-2023-12%5C%22%3Efailed%20to%20prop%20up%20oil%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20cutting%20production%2C%C2%A0in%20part%20because%20non-OPEC%20nations%20like%20the%20US%2C%20Brazil%2C%20and%20Guyana%20have%20kept%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Foil-market-outlook-opec-cuts-saudi-arabia-us-crude-supply-2023-12%5C%22%3Efilling%20the%20hole.%3C%2Fa%3E%20And%20fresh%20pledges%20from%20OPEC%2B%20to%20extend%20reductions%20into%20early%202024%20are%20falling%20flat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20say%20they're%20out%20of%20ammo%2C%20but%20they're%20kind%20of%20out%20of%20ammo%2C%26quot%3B%20Rebecca%20Babin%2C%20a%20senior%20equity%20trader%20for%20CIBC%20Private%20Wealth%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20say%20its%20ability%20to%20work%20together%20and%20manage%20the%20market%20is%20being%20questioned.%20OPEC's%20last%20meeting%20in%20November%20was%20chaotic%2C%20with%20members%20struggling%20to%20agree%20on%20cuts.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fetf%2Foil-prices-fall-after-angola-says-it-will-quit-opec-1032920542%5C%22%3EAngola%20announced%20it%20would%20quit%20the%20group%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20main%20risk%20for%20the%20market%20is%20the%20OPEC%20cohesion%20or%20lack%20thereof%20potentially%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Hunter%20Kornfeind%2C%20an%20oil%20analyst%20from%20Rapidan%20Energy%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaudi%20Arabia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOPEC's%20de%20facto%20leader%20has%20traditionally%20stepped%20in%20to%20restore%20order%20to%20the%20oil%20group%20and%20the%20overall%20market.%20One%20energy%20expert%20warned%20earlier%20that%20Saudi%20Arabia%20could%20wage%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Foil-outlook-saudi-arabia-opec-production-us-share-crude-supply-2023-12%5C%22%3Emarket%20share%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20US%20next%20year%20to%20regain%20control%20over%20oil%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Riyadh%20has%20other%20priorities%20that%20may%20prevent%20it%20from%20boosting%20supply%20to%20drive%20prices%20and%20profits%20down%2C%20forcing%20other%20producers%20to%20exit%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaudi%20Arabia%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20huge%20infrastructure%20projects%20coming%20on%20at%20the%20end%20of%20this%20decade%2C%20Homayoun%20Falakshahi%2C%20an%20oil%20analyst%20from%20research%20firm%20Kpler%2C%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20kingdom%20is%20hosting%20the%202029%20Asian%20Winter%20Games%2C%20the%202030%20World%20Expo%2C%20and%20the%202034%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%2C%20which%20will%20require%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20and%20the%20country's%20budget%20is%20dependent%20on%20oil.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20world's%20top%20oil%20importer%20has%20been%20roiled%20by%20a%20real%20estate%20crash%2C%20a%20debt%20crisis%2C%20and%20lackluster%20growth%20coming%20out%20of%20COVID%2C%20which%20have%20softened%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBabin%20recently%20said%20doubts%20about%20China's%20economy%20would%20be%20the%20oil%20market's%20biggest%20concern%20in%202024%2C%20followed%20by%20fear%20that%20US%20production%20will%20continue%20to%20outperform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20demand%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%20in%20China%20as%20new%20refineries%20ramp%20up%20activity%2C%20Falakshahi%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26q