20hotter-button%20pressing%20the%20creative%20community%20than%20authenticity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManowitz's%20insights%20are%20part%20of%20Business%20Insider's%20year-end%20leadership%20package%2C%20%26quot%3BLooking%20Ahead%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20digging%20into%20vision%2C%20strategy%2C%20and%20challenges%20across%20corporate%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20conversation%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20you%20most%20excited%20about%20for%202024%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20excited%20about%20getting%20our%20products%20and%20technologies%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20creators%20and%20seeing%20what%20they'll%20be%20creating%20that%20will%20go%20beyond%20our%20imagination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20you%20most%20worried%20about%20for%202024%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20empowering%20creators.%20For%20example%2C%20we're%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20identify%20people%20so%20we%20can%20autofocus%20better%20and%20make%20the%20camera%20easier%20for%20people%20to%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20we're%20thinking%20about%20how%20we%20can%20use%20AI%20to%20be%20a%20tool%20for%20creators%20and%20how%20we%20protect%20their%20rights.%20I'm%20worried%20about%20the%20converse%20act%20of%20that%20%E2%80%94%20the%20concern%20around%20this%20technology%20being%20used%20for%20bad%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20example%20is%20generative%20AI%20in%20imagery.%20It%20empowers%20creators%20to%20be%20more%20creative%20but%20also%20bears%20the%20risk%20of%20imagery%20being%20manipulated%20and%20misinterpreted.%20We've%20been%20working%20with%20the%20industry%20on%20in-camera-authenticity%20technology%20to%20validate%20the%20content's%20origins.%20Facts%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20was%20one%20thing%20you%20got%20right%20in%202023%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20closer%20to%20creators%2C%20listening%20to%20their%20feedback%2C%20and%20having%20their%20voice%20directly%20in%20our%20products.%20While%20their%20voice%20has%20always%20impacted%20our%20development%2C%20this%20year%20we%20saw%20great%20proof%20points%20of%20the%20deep%20impact%20they%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20several%20years%20the%20industry%20has%20trended%20toward%20making%20filmmaking%20more%20accessible%20and%20removing%20the%20gaps%20between%20what%20independent%20filmmakers%20could%20make%20and%20big-budget%20Hollywood%20films.%20The%20technology%20is%20advancing%20to%20align%20with%20what%20storytellers%20need%20and%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20our%20relationship%20with%20creators%2C%20we%20have%20a%20vested%20interest%20in%20the%20success%20of%20this%20community.%20The%20relationship%20is%20symbiotic.%20We%20know%20each%20other%2C%20we%20talk%20to%20each%20other%2C%20and%20we%20come%20together.%20We%20want%20to%20bring%20everybody%20in%20and%20find%20ways%20of%20connecting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20was%20one%20thing%20you%20got%20wrong%20in%202023%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnderestimating%20the%20lasting%20impact%20of%20COVID%20on%20our%20industry.%20From%20a%20social%20perspective%2C%20people's%20desire%20to%20go%20back%20out%20and%20experience%20the%20real%20world%20more.%20We%20underestimated%20the%20negative%20impact%20that%20would%20have%20on%20at-home%20entertainment%20products%20but%20then%20saw%20incredible%20demand%20for%20on-the-go%20products%20like%20headphones%20and%20cameras.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20stayed%20close%20to%20our%20creator%20community%20for%20that%20continuous%20feedback%20loop%2C%20which%20has%20been%20key.%20The%20camera-authenticity%20technology%20is%20a%20great%20example%20of%20how%20staying%20close%20to%20creators%20has%20kept%20us%20in%20line%20with%20the%20growing%20concern%20about%20fake%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsony-neal-manowitz-ai-c