ice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20chose%20never%20to%20make%20another%20resolution%20again%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeginning%20in%20my%20early%2030s%2C%20I%20resolved%20never%20to%20make%20another%20resolution.%20Instead%2C%20I%20chose%20to%20set%20intentions.%20This%20was%20a%20way%20for%20me%20to%20choose%20an%20emotionally%20based%20theme%20instead%20of%20a%20rigid%20goal.%20One%20year%2C%20I%20chose%20to%20concentrate%20on%20kindness%2C%20and%20then%20another%20year%20on%20thankfulness.%20This%20allowed%20me%20the%20space%20and%20flexibility%20to%20fail%20and%20redirect%20if%20needed.%20I%20finally%20had%20a%20New%20Year's%20tradition%20I%20felt%20good%20about%20%E2%80%94%20until%20my%20son%20got%20into%20the%20car%20as%20confused%20and%20claustrophobic%20as%20I'd%20felt%20in%20my%20childhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20had%20been%20to%20free%20myself%20from%20the%20pressure%20of%20participating%20in%20a%20custom%20that%20didn't%20work%20for%20me%20%E2%80%94%20not%20trap%20my%20kid%20in%20a%20place%20of%20icky%20feels.%20Wanting%20to%20help%2C%20I%20explained%20to%20him%20what%20it%20took%20me%20years%20to%20figure%20out%20%E2%80%94%20he%20had%20a%20choice.%20He%20could%20make%20resolutions%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20set%20intentions%20with%20us%2C%20or%20do%20both.%20I%20watched%20his%20eyes%20widen%2C%20and%20his%20fidgety%20fingers%20settle%20as%20he%20considered%20this%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20we%20created%20a%20new%20New%20Year's%20tradition.%20My%20son%20made%20his%20first%20New%20Year's%20Resolution%20last%20year%2C%20and%20to%20keep%20it%20old%20school%2C%20he%20also%20set%20an%20intention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20tells%20me%20he%20may%20eventually%20pick%20one%20favorite%20way%20to%20start%20the%20year%20or%20do%20both.%20He's%20not%20sure%20yet%2C%20but%20he%20assures%20me%20he%20knows%20he%20has%20a%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdont-like-making-new-years-r