r%20Mann%20on%20the%20tableau.%20This%20is%20not%20allowed%20as%20per%20protocol%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20tableau's%20rejection%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20drew%20a%20sharp%20retort%20from%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20who%20said%20he%20would%20quit%20politics%20if%20the%20state%20BJP%20president%20can%20prove%20his%20allegation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJakhar%20should%20give%20proof%20that%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20or%20Bhagwant%20Mann's%20photos%20were%20to%20be%20put%20on%20the%20tableau.%20Do%20they%20think%20we%20are%20mad%3F%20If%20Jakhar%20can%20prove%20it%2C%20I%20will%20quit%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20if%20he%20fails%2C%20%26quot%3Bhe%20should%20then%20also%20not%20enter%20Punjab%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWill%20(Prime%20Minister%20Narendra)%20Modi%20now%20choose%20which%20tableau%20is%20to%20be%20shown%20and%20which%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mann%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Defence%20Ministry%20source%20has%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20said%20there%20is%20a%20well-established%20system%20for%20the%20selection%20of%20tableaux.%20%26quot%3BThe%20tableaux%20proposals%20received%20from%20various%20States%2FUTs%20and%20Central%20Ministries%2FDepartments%20are%20evaluated%20in%20a%20series%20of%20meetings%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BExpert%20Committee%20for%20selection%20of%20tableaux%20comprising%20eminent%20persons%20in%20the%20field%20of%20art%2C%20culture%2C%20painting%2C%20sculpture%2C%20music%2C%20architecture%2C%20choreography%20etc.%20The%20Expert%20Committee%20examines%20the%20proposals%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20theme%2C%20concept%2C%20design%20and%20its%20visual%20impact%20before%20making%20its%20recommendations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMinistry%20of%20Defence%20Sources%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20allege