3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%20why%20were%20you%20asking%20me%3F%20Anyway%20you%20eat%20out%20%E2%80%93%20sometimes%20at%20Laadley%E2%80%99s%2C%20sometimes%20at%20that%20witch%20Naseeban%E2%80%99s%20house.%20How%20she%20has%20done%20black%20magic%20on%20you!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZaitoon%20nani%20clucked%20her%20tongue.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20a%20very%20bad%20influence%2C%20Sallu.%20You%20are%20wasting%20your%20time%20instead%20of%20finding%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFinding%20work%3F%E2%80%9D%20Salman%20scoffed.%20%E2%80%9CNani%2C%20why%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20ask%20Badey%20saheb%20to%20get%20me%20some%20decent%20work%3F%20I%20promise%20I%E2%80%99ll%20leave%20everything%20and%20focus.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20will%20he%20find%20you%20work%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20his%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20a%20big%20man.%20He%20knows%20everybody.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20it%20is%3A%20in%20our%20community%2C%20important%20people%20turn%20their%20faces%20away%20from%20people%20like%20me.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20meet%20our%20eyes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20embarrassment%2C%20They%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%2C%20so%20then%20what%20is%20the%20point%20of%20looking%3F%E2%80%9D%20At%20times%20Zaitoon%20nani%20could%20be%20very%20perceptive%20about%20her%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLook%20at%20Bulbhaddar%20babu%3A%20he%20has%20helped%20Shambhu%20and%20those%20two%20thugs%2C%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal.%20There%20is%20nobody%20to%20help%20us.%20Amma%2C%20why%20didn%E2%80%99t%20you%20at%20least%20send%20me%20to%20a%20proper%20school%3F%20She%20sent%20me%20to%20a%20madarsa%20to%20save%20money.%20Now%20I%20am%20stuck.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20a%2010th%C2%A0class%20certificate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20work%20night%20and%20day%20to%20feed%20you.%20Where%20was%20the%20money%20to%20send%20you%20to%20an%20English%20school%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20his%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C