ody%20had%20to%20go%20to%20see%20how%20soon%20they%20would%20return%20the%20body%2C%20so%20your%20Abba%20has%20gone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20is%20there%20a%20post%20mortem%3F%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20asked%20weakly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20killed!%20With%20his%20own%20steam%20iron%2C%20head%20smashed.%20There%20was%20a%20robbery%20too%20%E2%80%93%20the%20whole%20place%20is%20in%20disarray.%20Arshad%20had%20come%20to%20call%20your%20Abba%3B%20he%20told%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20walked%20with%20his%20mother%20to%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20only%20a%20few%20doors%20away%20from%20his%20restaurant%2C%20and%20further%20into%20the%20alley.%20They%20could%20hear%20begum%20saheba%E2%80%99s%20wailing%20even%20as%20they%20approached%20the%20house.%20An%20old%20durri%20had%20been%20spread%20in%20the%20gali%20outside%20but%20all%20the%20assembled%20men%20were%20standing%2C%20looking%20sombre%20and%20lost.%20Only%20the%20children%20from%20the%20madarsa%20were%20sitting%20on%20the%20durri%2C%20swinging%20back%20and%20forth%2C%20as%20they%20read%20the%20Quran%20in%20prayer%20for%20the%20departed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%20first%20went%20into%20the%20house%20with%20his%20mother%2C%20and%20watched%20from%20a%20distance%20as%20she%20embraced%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20wife.%20%E2%80%9CThree%20days%20I%20left%20him%20to%20go%20to%20my%20brother%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20and%20this%20is%20what%20happens.%20I%20took%20care%20of%20everything%20%E2%80%93%20his%20food%2C%20his%20health.%20I%20went%20away%20for%20three%20days%20and%20they%20have%20killed%20him%20%E2%80%93%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20they%20fed%20him.%20He%20had%20very%20bad%20asthma%20and%20now%20I%20find%20his%20inhaler%20is%20also%20lying%20at%20home.%20Nobody%20even%20took%20care%20to%20see%20his%20inhaler%20was%20with%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20accusingly%20and%20let%20out%20a%20moan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%2C%20in%20the%20gali%2C%20Arshad%20w