ents%E2%80%9D%20that%20talk%20about%20women%E2%80%99s%20upliftment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Punia%20urged%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20resume%20wrestling%20activities%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20as%20there%20have%20been%20no%20tournaments%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20the%20Olympic%20Games%20in%207%20months%20but%20no%20one%20seems%20serious%20about%20it%20while%20in%20the%20last%20four%20Olympics%2C%20wrestlers%20brought%20consecutive%20medals%2C%E2%80%9D%20Punia%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704005072000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31120945%2FScreenshot-2023-12-31-at-12.09.08-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fwrestler-vinesh-phogat-leaves-khel-ratna-arjuna-awards-on-kartavya-path-in-protest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She%20said%20that%20such%20awards%20were%20meaningless%20in%20a%20situation%20where%20women%20wrestlers%20were%20struggling%20to%20get%20justice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fwrestler-vinesh-phogat-leaves-khel-ratna-arjuna-awards-on-kartavya-path-in-protest%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20a%20Dark%20Year%2C%20Films%20and%20Series%20That%20Spoke%20of%20Idealism%2C%20Courage%20and%20Hope%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31120511%2FHM-films.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20year%20that%20we%20leave%20behind%20was%20a%20sombre%2C%20troubled%20one%20both%20for%20India%20and%20for%20much%20of%20the%20world.%20The%20politics%20of%20hate%20engulfed%20more%20and%20more%20people.%20Bombs%20pitilessly%20pounded%20children%20and%20hospitals%20in%20Gaza%20on%20a%20scale%20not%20seen%20this%20century%2C%20civilians%20picked%20up%20firearms%20against%20each%20other%20converting%20Manipur%20into%20an%20implacable%20war%20zone%2C%20and%20lynchings%20continued%20in%20India%2C%20barely%20noticed%20any%20more.%20Democracy%20faltered%2C%20inequality%20further%20soared%20and%20India%20fell%20even%20further%20in%20the%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%20rankings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20fitting%2C%20then%2C%20that%20the%20marker%20of%20the%20worthiest%20of%20Hindi%20films%20and%20shows%20of%202023%20was%20a%20common%20strain%20of%20dogged%20humanism%20%E2%80%93%20of%20idealism%2C%20courage%20and%20hope%20%E2%80%93%20even%20as%20they%20acknowledged%20the%20crises%20of%20inequality%2C%20injustice%20and%20hate%20that%20cobble%20the%20lives%20of%20ordinary%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20instructive%20that%20six%20of%20the%20nine%20films%20and%20shows%20listed%20here%20are%20based%20on%20true-life%20stories.%20And%20even%20those%20that%20are%20fictional%20are%20close%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20front%20line%20among%20my%20favourite%20films%20was%20one%20that%20came%20early%20in%20the%20year%2C%20Nandita%20Das%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EZwigato%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20narrative%20of%20aching%20tenderness%20and%20gentle%20rage.%20Das%20carefully%20observes%20the%20quiet%20struggles%2C%20the%20dignity%2C%20the%20resolve%2C%20the%20hurt%20and%20the%20determined%20love%20of%20Manas%20Mahto%2C%20a%20middle-aged%20food%20delivery%20man%2C%20and%20Pratima%20who%20steps%20out%20warily%20to%20share%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20burdens%2C%20as%20a%20masseuse%20to%20rich%20women%20in%20high-rise%20apartments%20and%20as%20a%20janitor%20in%20a%20mall.%20With%20luminous%20empathy%2C%20Kapil%20Sharma%20and%20Shahana%20Goswami%20portray%20how%20both%20try%20to%20hide%20from%20the%20other%20from%20the%20humiliations%2C%20the%20insults%20and%20disappointments%20that%20they%20endure%20as%20they%20daily%20grapple%20with%20the%20uncaring%2C%20unequal%20world%20of%20rich%20and%20middle-class%20India.%20Their%20unostentatious%20but%20steadfast%20love%20for%20each%20other%20and%20for%20those%20in%20their%20care%20forms%20the%20moral%20core%20of%20the%20film%2C%20and%20in%20the%20end%20its%20only%20fount%20of%20hope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31114728%2Fdownload-18.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31114728%2Fdownload-18.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31114728%2Fdownload-18-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31114728%2Fdownload-18-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691078%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKapil%20Sharma%20and%20Nandita%20Das%20on%20the%20sets%20of%20%E2%80%98Zwigato%E2%80%99.%20Photo%3A%20IMDB%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20this%20same%20stubborn%20humanism%20that%20drew%20me%20to%20the%20mini-series%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Railway%20Men%3A%20The%20Untold%20Story%20of%20Bhopal%201984%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecompellingly%20directed%20by%20Shiv%20Rawail.%20It%20chooses%20to%20tell%20the%20story%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20worst%20industrial%20disaster%20that%20took%2015%2C000%20lives%20and%20ravaged%20several%20hundred%20thousand%20others%20by%20centre-staging%20narratives%20of%20the%20heroic%20exertions%20of%20railway%20officials%20who%20risked%20their%20lives%20to%20save%20the%20lives%20of%20hundreds%20of%20others.%20The%20writing%20and%20visualisation%20are%20emotive%20and%20eloquent%20as%20they%20recall%20the%20grisly%20events%20of%20that%20fateful%20winter%20night%20in%20Bhopal%20when%20poisonous%20gas%20leaked%20due%20to%20criminal%20neglect%20by%20the%20Union%20Carbide%20and%20people%20began%20to%20drop%20dead%20in%20thousands.%20There%20are%20at%20least%20two%20points%20of%20departure%20for%20the%20miniseries.%20The%20first%20of%20these%20is%20the%20real-life%20story%20of%20Ghulam%20Dastigar%2C%20the%20Deputy%20Station%20Master%20of%20Bhopal%20Junction%20who%2C%20unmindful%20of%20his%20own%20safety%2C%20did%20not%20abandon%20his%20post%20and%20ensured%20that%20several%20trains%20to%20Bhopal%20that%20night%20were%20diverted.%20If%20he%20had%20not%2C%20hundreds%20more%20would%20have%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20real-life%20story%20woven%20into%20the%20chronicle%20is%20of%20Rajkumar%20Keswani%2C%20a%20journalist%20who%20had%20warned%20authorities%20after%20his%20friend%20had%20died%20of%20a%20gas%20leak%20about%20the%20dangers%20that%20the%20plant%20posed%20three%20years%20before%20the%20disaster.%20But%20no%20one%20paid%20heed.%20There%20are%20other%20stories%20as%20well%2C%20including%20of%20a%20railway%20worker%20on%20his%20first%20day%20of%20employment%2C%20who%20dies%20saving%20many%20others.%20In%20the%20retelling%20of%20the%20story%20of%20the%20disaster%2C%20the%20horror%20of%20the%20appalling%20crimes%20of%20those%20who%20risked%20the%20lives%20of%20thousands%20for%20the%20cynical%20pursuit%20of%20profit%20and%20the%20complicity%20of%20people%20in%20authority%20is%20mitigated%20by%20the%20inspiring%20courage%20and%20gallantry%20of%20ordinary%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Big%20Action%2C%20Small%2C%20Intimate%20Stories%20and%20Some%20Subversive%20Turns%3A%20The%20Best%20Hindi%20Films%20of%202023%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fbig-action-small-intimate-stories-subversion-best-hindi-films-2023%5C%22%3EBig%20Action%2C%20Small%2C%20Intimate%20Stories%20and%20Some%20Subversive%20Turns%3A%20The%20Best%20Hindi%20Films%20of%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20different%20kind%20of%20courage%20is%20the%20moral%20core%20of%20another%20miniseries%20%3Cem%3ETrial%20by%20Fire%20%3C%2Fem%3Eabout%20another%20tragedy%20in%201997%2C%20in%20which%20a%20fire%20accident%20in%20a%20cinema%20hall%20Uphaar%20Cinema%20in%20South%20Delhi%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%2059%20people%20and%20serious%20injuries%20to%20103%20others.%20The%20story%20is%20recounted%20here%20through%20the%20staggeringly%20dogged%20unwavering%20struggle%20stretched%20over%20two%20decades%20of%20Neelam%20Krishnamoorthy%20and%20her%20husband%20Shekhar%2C%20who%20had%20lost%20both%20their%20children%20in%20the%20fire%20accident.%20Their%20profound%20loss%20and%20sorrow%20drives%20Neelam%2C%20supported%20steadfastly%20by%20her%20husband%2C%20to%20relentlessly%2C%20even%20obsessively%20pursue%20justice%20from%20the%20courts.%20The%20criminal%20cases%20against%20the%20cinema%20owners%2C%20the%20Ansal%20brothers%2C%20who%20had%20violated%20elementary%20safety%20norms%2C%20and%20the%20managers%20of%20the%20theatre%20move%20at%20a%20glacial%20pace%20through%20the%20Kafkaesque%20maze%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20judicial%20system.%20In%20the%20end%20the%20courts%20let%20off%20those%20criminally%20guilty%20of%20causing%20so%20many%20deaths%20all%20too%20lightly.%20Justice%20fails%20Neelam%20and%20Shekhar%2C%20but%20they%20are%20victorious%20in%20the%20ways%20they%20uphold%20the%20tenacity%20of%20the%20human%20spirit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31115205%2FTrial-By-Fire.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31115205%2FTrial-By-Fire.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31115205%2FTrial-By-Fire-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31115205%2FTrial-By-Fire-1024x576.jpe