ppression%2C%20sometimes%20through%20religious%20hatred%2C%20sometimes%20through%20class%20inequality%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20each%20time%20this%20moral%20arc%20of%20humanism%20that%20pierces%20through%20the%20blackness.%20In%20this%20year%20of%20enveloping%20darkness%2C%20I%20am%20grateful%20that%20the%20best%20of%20popular%20art%20celebrates%20idealism%2C%20courage%20and%20love%20so%20that%20we%20still%20can%20hope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fharsh-mander%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Harsh%20Mander%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarsh%20Mander%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20social%20worker%20and%20writer.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704004561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31120511%2FHM-films.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fin-a-dark-year-films-and-series-that-spoke-of-idealism-courage-and-hope%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Zwigato%2C%20Trial%20by%20Fire%2C%20Dahaad%20and%20Afwaah%20were%20some%20of%20the%20films%20that%20reflected%20the%20travails%20of%20ordinary%20folk.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fin-a-dark-year-films-and-series-that-spoke-of-idealism-courage-and-hope%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kim%20Jong%20Un%20makes%20nuclear%20weapon%20pledge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704004440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F70x70%2Fskynews-north-korean-kim-jong-un_6408208.jpg%3F20231231074454%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fkim-jong-un-warns-war-is-realistic-reality-as-he-pledges-to-build-more-nuclear-weapons-in-2024-13039937%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22North%20Korea's%20leader%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%20has%20pledged%20to%20launch%20three%20new%20spy%20satellites%2C%20build%20mil