mations%20that%20the%20government%20and%20others%20make%20over%20needs%20of%20the%20population%2C%20as%20the%20Census%20is%20the%20largest%20public%20body%20of%20data%20about%20the%20country%20available%20and%20updated.%20It%20may%20even%20render%20those%20seen%20as%20needing%20extra%20care%20under%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act%20among%20the%20uncounted%20and%20therefore%20not%20helped%20by%20government%20schemes.%20The%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%20passed%20in%20the%20special%20session%20of%20parliament%20is%20contingent%20on%20the%20next%20delimitation%2C%20which%20depends%20on%20the%20next%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20latest%20decision%20of%20the%20Addl.%20Registrar%20General%20of%20India%20regarding%20the%20freezing%20of%20administrative%20boundaries%20until%20October%202024%20is%20perplexing%20as%20no%20reasons%20have%20been%20publicised%20for%20the%20same.%20We%2C%20the%20citizenry%20are%20completely%20in%20the%20dark%20about%20the%20plans%20for%20conducting%20the%20long%20overdue%20decennial%20census.%202023%20was%20a%20largely%20Covid%20infection%20free%20year%20but%20census%20data%20collection%20exercise%20was%20not%20initiated.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20up-to-date%20data%2C%20how%20will%20the%20State%20and%20Central%20governments%20plan%20developmental%20programmes%20and%20poverty%20eradication%20schemes%20is%20a%20billion%20dollar%20question.%20The%20non-disclosure%20of%20certain%20annual%20reports%20needs%20to%20be%20seen%20in%20light%20of%20the%20trend%20that%20has%20emerged%20over%20recent%20years%20of%20stalling%20the%20publication%20of%20crucial%20demographic%20and%20economic%20statistics%20giving%20some%20technical%20excuse%20or%20the%20other%2C%E2%80%9D%20transparency%20rights%20activist%20Venkatesh%20Nayak%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20Census%2C%20the%20office%20of%20the%20RGI%20and%20the%20Census%20Commissioner%20of%20India%20have%20also%20not%20released%20two%20important%20reports%20on%20the%20registration%20of%20births%2C%20deaths%2C%20and%20causes%20of%20deaths%20for%20the%20years%202021%2C%202022%20and%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20writes%20that%20the%20report%20on%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcensusindia.gov.in%2Fnada%2Findex.php%2Fcatalog%2F42542%5C%22%3EVital%20Statistics%20of%20India%20Based%20On%20The%20Civil%20Registration%20System%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20for%202020%20was%20only%20released%20in%20May%202022.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20vital%20statistics%20are%20invaluable%20for%20planning%2C%C2%A0monitoring%20and%20evaluating%20various%20programmes%20related%20to%20primary%20health%20care%2C%20family%20planning%2C%C2%A0maternal%20and%20child%20health%2C%20education%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20cites%20the%20report%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcensusindia.gov.in%2Fnada%2Findex.php%2Fcatalog%2F42681%2Fdownload%2F46350%2FAnnual_Report_on_MCCD_2020.pdf%5C%22%3EReport%20On%20Medical%20Certification%20Of%20Cause%20of%20Death%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20was%20last%20released%20for%20the%20year%202020.%20This%20report%20carries%20statistics%20on%20the%20causes%20of%20deaths%2C%20cross-tabulating%20them%20by%20age%20and%20sex%20of%20the%20deceased.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20wide%20divergence%2C%20almost%20ten-fold%2C%20between%20India%E2%80%99s%20reported%20figures%20on%20COVID-19%20and%20that%20estimated%20globally%20by%20the%20WHO.%20The%20official%20document%20would%20bring%20more%20clarity%20on%20this%20but%20it%20remains%20unreleased.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704004202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F07202552%2FScreenshot-2022-02-07-at-8.25.47-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-census-till-at-least-october-2024-ninth-extension-of-deadline-the-hindu%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%222021%20was%20the%20first%20time%20the%20decennia