ion%2C%20should%20immediately%20cease%20all%20acts%20and%20measures%20in%20breach%20of%20those%20obligations%20and%20take%20a%20number%20of%20related%20actions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20rejected%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20allegations%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccollaborating%E2%80%9D%20with%20terrorists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSouth%20Africa%20is%20collaborating%20with%20a%20terrorist%20group%20that%20calls%20for%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20destruction%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20Israeli%20Foreign%20Ministry.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20of%20Gaza%20are%20not%20an%20enemy%20of%20Israel%2C%20who%20is%20making%20efforts%20to%20limit%20harm%20to%20non-combatants.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20classifies%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhamas%2Ft-19034915%5C%22%3EHamas%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0as%20a%20terrorist%20organization%2C%20as%20do%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20Germany%20and%20several%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2085%25%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%E2%80%99s%20population%20has%20been%20displaced%20in%20the%20conflict.%20The%20Health%20Ministry%20in%20the%20Hamas-controlled%20territory%20has%20said%20that%20over%2021%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20and%20fighting%20since%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fsouth-african-lawmakers-vote-to-shut-israels-embassy%2Fa-67458372%5C%22%3ESouth%20African%20lawmakers%20voted%20to%20suspend%20formal%20ties%20with%20Israel%20and%20close%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20embassy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20move%20needs%20to%20be%20approved%20by%20President%20Cyril%20Ramaphosa%20to%20take%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Palestinian%20Authority%E2%80%99s%20Foreign%20Ministry%20has%20welcomed%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20accusation%20of%20%E2%80%9Cgenocide%E2%80%9D%20against%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fisr